n73: ## References\n74: \n75: - Spec: `changes/AR-036/spec.md`\n76: - Delta Spec: `changes/AR-036/delta-spec.md`\n77: - Proposal: `changes/AR-036/proposal.md`\n78: - Tasks: `changes/AR-036/tasks.md`\n79: - integrations directory: `integrations/`\n80: - [TO BE FILLED: Add relevant references]\n\n(End of file - total 80 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-036 — Dify 插件集成 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-036 — Dify 插件集成 |\n| Module | integrations |\n| Language | Python |\n| Size | M |\n| Stage | ST-1 (completed) |\n\n---\n\n## Architecture\n\n[TO BE FILLED: Add architecture diagrams and high-level design]\n\n---\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-036/design.md","time":{"start":1775904137497,"end":1775904137522}}}}
