{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775904302389,"sessionID":"ses_283ddf084ffeVDO3EJ8GNUANRn","part":{"id":"prt_d7c25246f001McJVHUyxdfxY3q","messageID":"msg_d7c22b8f1001n9aSUVTWX3Y71o","sessionID":"ses_283ddf084ffeVDO3EJ8GNUANRn","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-5c00b672710c493e88949830487cf5af","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-042/design.md","content":"# AR-042 — Docusaurus 文档站框架 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-042 — Docusaurus 文档站框架 |\n| Module | docs |\n| Language | TypeScript |\n| Size | M |\n| Stage | ST-1 (completed) |\n\n---\n\n## Architecture\n\n### Component Overview\n\n```\ndocs/\n├── docusaurus.config.ts     # Core configuration (site metadata, plugins, theme)\n├── sidebars.ts              # Sidebar navigation structure\n├── package.json             # npm dependencies and scripts\n├── tsconfig.json            # TypeScript configuration\n├── src/\n│   ├── pages/\n│   │   └── index.tsx        # Homepage component\n│   └── css/\n│   │   └── custom.css       # Custom styles and branding\n│   └── components/          # Custom React components\n│   └── theme/               # Theme overrides\n├── docs/\n│   ├── architecture/\n│   │   ├── overview.md      # System architecture overview\n│   │   ├── sandbox.md       # Sandbox orchestration details\n│   │   ├── session-routing.md\n│   │   └── idle-cleanup.md\n│   ├── api/\n│   │   ├── sdk-python/\n│   │   │   ├── client.md    # Python SDK API reference\n│   │   │   └── examples.md\n│   │   └── client-go/\n│   │       ├── overview.md  # Go client API reference\n│   │       └── examples.md\n│   ├── deployment/\n│   │   ├── kubernetes.md    # K8s deployment guide\n│   │   ├── helm-chart.md    # Helm chart parameters\n│   │   └── configuration.md\n│   ├── getting-started/\n│   │   ├── installation.md  # Prerequisites and setup\n│   │   ├── first-sandbox.md # Quick-start tutorial\n│   │   ├── configuration.md\n│   │   └── next-steps.md\n│   └── changelog/\n│       ├── index.md         # Release history\n│       ├── v0.1.0.md\n│       └── v0.2.0.md\n├── static/\n│   ├── img/\n│   │   ├── logo.svg         # Project logo\n│   │   ├── architecture-diagrams/\n│   │   └── screenshots/\n│   └── favicon.ico\n├── i18n/\n│   ├── en/                  # English translations\n│   └── zh-Hans/             # Chinese translations\n└── build/                   # Production build output\n```\n\n### Component Interactions\n\n```\n┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                           Docusaurus Site Architecture                         │\n├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│                                                                               │\n│  ┌─────────────────────┐     ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │\n│  │ docusaurus.config.ts│────▶│              Plugin Chain                    │ │\n│  │                     │     │  ┌─────────────┐  ┌───────────────────────┐  │ │\n│  │ - siteMetadata      │     │  │ preset-     │  │ theme-search-algolia  │  │ │\n│  │ - themeConfig       │     │  │ classic     │  │ plugin-search-local   │  │ │\n│  │ - plugins           │     │  └─────────────┘  └───────────────────────┘  │ │\n│  │ - presets           │     │  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐ │ │\n│  └─────────────────────┘     │  │ content-docs, content-blog, sitemap    │ │ │\n│                              │  └─────────────────────────────────────────┘ │ │\n│                              └─────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │\n│                                                                               │\n│  ┌─────────────────────┐     ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │\n│  │ sidebars.ts         │────▶│              Navigation                     │ │\n│  │                     │     │  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐ │ │\n│  │ - gettingStarted    │     │  │ Sidebar Categories                      │ │ │\n│  │ - architecture      │     │  │  ├── Getting Started                    │ │ │\n│  │ - api               │     │  │  ├── Architecture                       │ │ │\n│  │ - deployment        │     │  │  ├── API Reference                      │ │ │\n│  │ - changelog         │     │  │  ├── Deployment                         │ │ │\n│  │                     │     │  │  └── Changelog                          │ │ │\n│  └─────────────────────┘     │  └─────────────────────────────────────────┘ │ │\n│                              └─────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │\n│                                                                               │\n│  ┌─────────────────────┐     ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │\n│  │ src/pages/          │────▶│              Page Rendering                 │ │\n│  │                     │     │  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐ │ │\n│  │ - index.tsx         │     │  │ React Pages                             │ │ │\n│  │ - custom pages      │     │  │  ├── Homepage (Hero + CTA)              │ │ │\n│  │                     │     │  │  ├── Version Selector                   │ │ │\n│  │                     │     │  │  └── Language Switcher                  │ │ │\n│  └─────────────────────┘     │  └─────────────────────────────────────────┘ │ │\n│                              └─────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │\n│                                                                               │\n│  ┌─────────────────────┐     ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │\n│  │ docs/**/*.md        │────▶│              Content Processing             │ │\n│  │                     │     │  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐ │ │\n│  │ - frontmatter       │     │  │ Markdown → React                        │ │ │\n│  │ - Mermaid diagrams  │     │  │  ├── MDX processing                     │ │ │\n│  │ - code examples     │     │  │  ├── Mermaid rendering                  │ │ │\n│  │                     │     │  │  ├── Code highlighting                  │ │ │\n│  └─────────────────────┘     │  └─────────────────────────────────────────┘ │ │\n│                              └─────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │\n│                                                                               │\n└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n### Build and Deployment Flow\n\n```\n┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                          Build & Deployment Pipeline                          │\n├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│                                                                               │\n│  ┌───────────────────┐                                                       │\n│  │ Source Files      │                                                       │\n│  │ docs/**/*.md      │                                                       │\n│  │ src/**/*.tsx      │                                                       │\n│  └───────────────────┘                                                       │\n│           │                                                                   │\n│           ▼                                                                   │\n│  ┌───────────────────┐     ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n│  │ npm run build     │────▶│              Build Steps                     │  │\n│  │                   │     │  1. TypeScript compilation                   │  │\n│  │                   │     │  2. Markdown → React components              │  │\n│  │                   │     │  3. Asset optimization                       │  │\n│  │                   │     │  4. Static HTML generation                   │  │\n│  │                   │     │  5. Search index creation                    │  │\n│  └───────────────────┘     └─────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n│           │                                                                   │\n│           ▼                                                                   │\n│  ┌───────────────────┐                                                       │\n│  │ build/            │                                                       │\n│  │ (static site)     │                                                       │\n│  └───────────────────┘                                                       │\n│           │                                                                   │\n│           ▼                                                                   │\n│  ┌───────────────────┐     ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n│  │ GitHub Actions    │────▶│              Deploy                          │  │\n│  │ docs.yml          │     │  gh-pages branch OR custom domain            │  │\n│  └───────────────────┘     └─────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n│                                                                               │\n└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n## Data Structures\n\n### Docusaurus Configuration Interface\n\n```typescript\ninterface DocusaurusConfig {\n  title: string;\n  tagline: string;\n  url: string;\n  baseUrl: string;\n  favicon: string;\n  organizationName: string;\n  projectName: string;\n  trailingSlash: boolean;\n  onBrokenLinks: 'throw' | 'warn';\n  onBrokenMarkdownLinks: 'throw' | 'warn';\n  i18n: {\n    defaultLocale: string;\n    locales: string[];\n  };\n  presets: PresetConfig[];\n  plugins: PluginConfig[];\n  themeConfig: ThemeConfig;\n}\n```\n\n### Theme Configuration\n\n```typescript\ninterface ThemeConfig {\n  navbar: NavbarConfig;\n  footer: FooterConfig;\n  prism: PrismConfig;\n  algolia?: AlgoliaConfig;\n  docs: DocsThemeConfig;\n}\n\ninterface NavbarConfig {\n  title: string;\n  logo: LogoConfig;\n  items: NavbarItem[];\n}\n\ninterface NavbarItem {\n  type?: 'doc' | 'docSidebar' | 'docsVersion' | 'localeDropdown' | 'search';\n  label: string;\n  to?: string;\n  href?: string;\n  docsPluginId?: string;\n  sidebarId?: string;\n  position?: 'left' | 'right';\n}\n\ninterface FooterConfig {\n  style: 'dark' | 'light';\n  links: FooterLinkSection[];\n  logo?: LogoConfig;\n  copyright: string;\n}\n\ninterface FooterLinkSection {\n  title: string;\n  items: FooterLink[];\n}\n\ninterface FooterLink {\n  label: string;\n  to?: string;\n  href?: string;\n}\n```\n\n### Sidebar Configuration\n\n```typescript\ninterface SidebarsConfig {\n  gettingStarted: SidebarItem[];\n  architecture: SidebarItem[];\n  api: SidebarItem[];\n  deployment: SidebarItem[];\n  changelog: SidebarItem[];\n}\n\ninterface SidebarItem {\n  type: 'doc' | 'category' | 'link' | 'generated-index';\n  id?: string;\n  label: string;\n  items?: SidebarItem[];\n  link?: {\n    type: 'generated-index' | 'doc';\n    id?: string;\n    slug?: string;\n    description?: string;\n  };\n  className?: string;\n  customProps?: Record<string, unknown>;\n}\n```\n\n### Document Frontmatter Schema\n\n```typescript\ninterface DocFrontmatter {\n  id: string;\n  title: string;\n  description?: string;\n  slug?: string;\n  sidebar_label?: string;\n  sidebar_position?: number;\n  hide_title?: boolean;\n  hide_table_of_contents?: boolean;\n  toc_min_heading_level?: number;\n  toc_max_heading_level?: number;\n  pagination_prev?: string | null;\n  pagination_next?: string | null;\n  last_update?: {\n    date: string;\n    author: string;\n  };\n  keywords?: string[];\n  tags?: string[];\n}\n```\n\n### i18n Locale Configuration\n\n```typescript\ninterface LocaleConfig {\n  label: string;\n  direction: 'ltr' | 'rtl';\n  htmlLang: string;\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## API Contracts\n\n### Site Configuration Contract\n\n**docusaurus.config.ts Required Fields:**\n\n| Field | Type | Required | Default | Description |\n|-------|------|----------|---------|-------------|\n| `title` | `string` | Yes | - | Site title displayed in navbar |\n| `tagline` | `string` | Yes | - | Site description for SEO |\n| `url` | `string` | Yes | - | Production deployment URL |\n| `baseUrl` | `string` | Yes | `/` | Base path for deployment |\n| `favicon` | `string` | Yes | - | Relative path to favicon |\n| `organizationName` | `string` | Yes | - | GitHub organization name |\n| `projectName` | `string` | Yes | - | GitHub project name |\n\n**Contract:**\n- `url` SHALL be `https://volcano-sh.github.io`\n- `baseUrl` SHALL be `/agentcube/`\n- `title` SHALL be `AgentCube`\n- `tagline` SHALL describe sandbox orchestration purpose\n\n### Navigation Contract\n\n**Navbar Items Required:**\n\n| Label | Target | Position |\n|-------|--------|----------|\n| Documentation | `/docs` | left |\n| API Reference | `/docs/api` | left |\n| Architecture | `/docs/architecture` | left |\n| Deployment | `/docs/deployment` | left |\n| Getting Started | `/docs/getting-started` | left |\n| GitHub | `https://github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` | right |\n\n**Contract:**\n- Each navbar item SHALL have valid `to` or `href`\n- Navbar SHALL be responsive for mobile devices\n- Logo SHALL link to homepage\n\n### Sidebar Contract\n\n**Sidebar Categories Required:**\n\n| Category | Document IDs | Order |\n|----------|--------------|-------|\n| `gettingStarted` | `installation`, `first-sandbox`, `configuration`, `next-steps` | 1 |\n| `architecture` | `overview`, `sandbox`, `session-routing`, `idle-cleanup` | 2 |\n| `api` | `sdk-python/client`, `sdk-python/examples`, `client-go/overview`, `client-go/examples` | 3 |\n| `deployment` | `kubernetes`, `helm-chart`, `configuration` | 4 |\n| `changelog` | `index`, `v0.1.0`, `v0.2.0` | 5 |\n\n**Contract:**\n- Sidebar SHALL auto-generate from `docs/**/*.md` files\n- Items SHALL be ordered by `sidebar_position` frontmatter\n- Categories SHALL have collapsible functionality\n\n### Homepage Contract\n\n**Homepage Components Required:**\n\n| Component | Description |\n|-----------|-------------|\n| Hero Section | Project title, tagline, logo |\n| CTA Buttons | \"Get Started\" → `/docs/getting-started/installation`, \"View on GitHub\" → external |\n| Features Grid | 3-4 feature highlights with icons |\n| Footer | Links, copyright |\n\n**Contract:**\n- Homepage SHALL use Docusaurus `@theme/Layout` wrapper\n- Hero SHALL include gradient background\n- CTA buttons SHALL be prominent and accessible\n\n---\n\n## Error Handling\n\n### Build Error Categories\n\n| Error Type | Source | Handling | Recovery |\n|------------|--------|----------|----------|\n| Broken Link | Markdown link resolution | Build fails with error | Fix link path |\n| Broken Markdown Link | Markdown link resolution | Build fails with error | Fix markdown link |\n| Invalid Frontmatter | YAML parsing | Build fails with error | Fix YAML syntax |\n| TypeScript Error | TSX compilation | Build fails with error | Fix TS errors |\n| Plugin Error | Plugin initialization | Build fails with error | Fix plugin config |\n| Asset Missing | Static file resolution | Build warning/fail | Add missing asset |\n\n### Build Validation Errors\n\n```typescript\nenum BuildErrorLevel {\n  THROW = 'throw',\n  WARN = 'warn',\n  IGNORE = 'ignore'\n}\n\ninterface BrokenLinkError {\n  type: 'broken-link' | 'broken-markdown-link';\n  link: string;\n  file: string;\n  remediation: string;\n}\n```\n\n**Configuration:**\n- `onBrokenLinks: 'throw'` - Hard fail on broken links\n- `onBrokenMarkdownLinks: 'throw'` - Hard fail on broken markdown links\n\n### Runtime Error Handling\n\n| Scenario | Error | User Impact | Mitigation |\n|----------|-------|-------------|------------|\n| Search unavailable | Algolia API error | Search disabled | Fallback to local search |\n| Language file missing | Missing i18n JSON | Default locale used | Log warning, continue |\n| Image not found | 404 on static assets | Missing image placeholder | Use placeholder, log warning |\n| Version not found | Invalid version path | 404 page | Redirect to latest |\n\n### CI/CD Error Handling\n\n```yaml\n# docs.yml workflow error handling\njobs:\n  build:\n    steps:\n      - name: Build\n        run: npm run build\n        continue-on-error: false\n        \n      - name: Check build output\n        run: |\n          if [ ! -d \"build\" ]; then\n            echo \"Build directory not found\"\n            exit 1\n          fi\n          \n      - name: Validate links\n        run: npm run check-links || echo \"Link check completed\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### Unit Tests\n\n| Test | File | Scenario | Verification |\n|------|------|----------|--------------|\n| Config validation | `__tests__/config.test.ts` | Required fields present | All fields validated |\n| Sidebar structure | `__tests__/sidebar.test.ts` | Categories defined correctly | Navigation works |\n| Navbar items | `__tests__/navbar.test.ts` | Links are valid | No broken links |\n| Homepage render | `__tests__/index.test.ts` | Hero and CTA present | Components render |\n| TypeScript config | `__tests__/tsconfig.test.ts` | Strict mode enabled | TS compiles |\n| i18n setup | `__tests__/i18n.test.ts` | Locale directories exist | i18n works |\n\n### Test Pattern\n\n```typescript\ndescribe('DocusaurusConfig', () => {\n  it('should have required fields', () => {\n    const config = require('../docusaurus.config');\n    \n    expect(config.title).toBeDefined();\n    expect(config.tagline).toBeDefined();\n    expect(config.url).toBeDefined();\n    expect(config.baseUrl).toBeDefined();\n    expect(config.favicon).toBeDefined();\n    expect(config.organizationName).toBeDefined();\n    expect(config.projectName).toBeDefined();\n  });\n  \n  it('should have valid navbar items', () => {\n    const config = require('../docusaurus.config');\n    const items = config.themeConfig.navbar.items;\n    \n    expect(items.length).toBeGreaterThan(0);\n    items.forEach(item => {\n      expect(item.label).toBeDefined();\n      expect(item.to || item.href).toBeDefined();\n    });\n  });\n  \n  it('should have valid sidebar categories', () => {\n    const sidebars = require('../sidebars');\n    \n    expect(sidebars.gettingStarted).toBeDefined();\n    expect(sidebars.architecture).toBeDefined();\n    expect(sidebars.api).toBeDefined();\n    expect(sidebars.deployment).toBeDefined();\n    expect(sidebars.changelog).toBeDefined();\n  });\n});\n```\n\n### Integration Tests\n\n| Test | Scenario | Verification |\n|------|----------|--------------|\n| Local server start | `npm run start` | Dev server on port 3000 |\n| Production build | `npm run build` | Build directory created |\n| Links resolution | Navigate all pages | No 404 errors |\n| Search functionality | Query search bar | Results returned |\n| i18n switching | Change locale | Content translated |\n| Mermaid rendering | View architecture pages | Diagrams rendered |\n| Code highlighting | View API pages | Syntax highlighted |\n\n### End-to-End Tests (Playwright/Cypress)\n\n```typescript\ndescribe('Docs Site E2E', () => {\n  it('homepage should render correctly', async () => {\n    await page.goto('http://localhost:3000');\n    \n    await expect(page.locator('.hero__title')).toHaveText('AgentCube');\n    await expect(page.locator('.hero__cta')).toBeVisible();\n    await expect(page.locator('a[href=\"/docs/getting-started\"]')).toBeVisible();\n  });\n  \n  it('sidebar navigation should work', async () => {\n    await page.goto('http://localhost:3000/docs/architecture/overview');\n    \n    await page.click('[data-testid=\"sidebar-item-getting-started\"]');\n    await expect(page).toHaveURL(/\\/docs\\/getting-started/);\n  });\n  \n  it('search should return results', async () => {\n    await page.goto('http://localhost:3000');\n    await page.fill('.search-bar input', 'sandbox');\n    \n    await expect(page.locator('.search-result')).toBeVisible();\n  });\n});\n```\n\n### Test Coverage Goals\n\n| Area | Target Coverage |\n|------|------------------|\n| Config validation | 100% |\n| Navigation links | 100% (all links valid) |\n| Homepage components | >80% |\n| Build process | >70% |\n| Search integration | >60% |\n\n### Validation Commands\n\n```bash\nnpm run build                    # Production build test\nnpm run start                    # Dev server test\nnpm run typecheck                # TypeScript validation\nnpm run lint                     # ESLint validation\nnpx playwright test              # E2E tests\nlinkinator build/ --recursive    # Link validation\n```\n\n---\n\n## File Structure\n\n### Core Files\n\n| File | Action | Purpose |\n|------|--------|---------|\n| `docs/docusaurus.config.ts` | create | Site configuration |\n| `docs/sidebars.ts` | create | Sidebar structure |\n| `docs/package.json` | create | Dependencies and scripts |\n| `docs/tsconfig.json` | create | TypeScript configuration |\n| `docs/.gitignore` | create | Ignore build output |\n| `docs/README.md` | create | Docs project README |\n\n### Source Files\n\n| File | Action | Purpose |\n|------|--------|---------|\n| `docs/src/pages/index.tsx` | create | Homepage component |\n| `docs/src/css/custom.css` | create | Custom styling |\n| `docs/src/components/` | create | Custom React components |\n| `docs/src/theme/` | create | Theme overrides |\n\n### Documentation Content\n\n| File | Action | Source |\n|------|--------|--------|\n| `docs/docs/architecture/overview.md` | create | From `design.md` |\n| `docs/docs/architecture/sandbox.md` | create | From `sandbox-orchestration/design.md` |\n| `docs/docs/architecture/session-routing.md` | create | From `session-routing/design.md` |\n| `docs/docs/architecture/idle-cleanup.md` | create | From `idle-cleanup/design.md` |\n| `docs/docs/api/sdk-python/client.md` | create | From `sdk-python/` docs |\n| `docs/docs/api/client-go/overview.md` | create | From `client-go/` docs |\n| `docs/docs/deployment/kubernetes.md` | create | From `deployment/design.md` |\n| `docs/docs/deployment/helm-chart.md` | create | From `manifests/` charts |\n| `docs/docs/getting-started/installation.md` | create | New content |\n| `docs/docs/getting-started/first-sandbox.md` | create | New content |\n| `docs/docs/changelog/index.md` | create | From GitHub Releases |\n\n### Static Assets\n\n| File | Action | Purpose |\n|------|--------|---------|\n| `docs/static/img/logo.svg` | create | Project logo |\n| `docs/static/img/favicon.ico` | create | Browser favicon |\n| `docs/static/img/architecture/*.svg` | create | Architecture diagrams |\n\n### i18n Files\n\n| File | Action | Purpose |\n|------|--------|---------|\n| `docs/i18n/en/` | create | English translations |\n| `docs/i18n/zh-Hans/` | create | Chinese translations |\n\n### CI/CD Files\n\n| File | Action | Purpose |\n|------|--------|---------|\n| `.github/workflows/docs.yml` | create | GitHub Actions workflow |\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n### npm Dependencies\n\n| Package | Version | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|---------|\n| `@docusaurus/core` | `3.x` | Docusaurus core framework |\n| `@docusaurus/preset-classic` | `3.x` | Classic preset (docs, blog, pages) |\n| `@docusaurus/theme-search-algolia` | `3.x` | Algolia search integration |\n| `@docusaurus/plugin-search-local` | `latest` | Local search fallback |\n| `@docusaurus/module-type-aliases` | `3.x` | TypeScript type definitions |\n| `@docusaurus/types` | `3.x` | Core type definitions |\n| `react` | `18.x` | React frontend framework |\n| `react-dom` | `18.x` | React DOM renderer |\n| `typescript` | `5.x` | TypeScript compiler |\n\n### Development Dependencies\n\n| Package | Version | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|---------|\n| `@types/react` | `18.x` | React type definitions |\n| `@types/react-dom` | `18.x` | React DOM type definitions |\n| `@typescript-eslint/eslint-plugin` | `latest` | TypeScript ESLint |\n| `@typescript-eslint/parser` | `latest` | ESLint TypeScript parser |\n| `eslint` | `8.x` | JavaScript linter |\n| `prettier` | `3.x` | Code formatter |\n| `linkinator` | `latest` | Link checker |\n\n### External Resources\n\n| Resource | URL | Purpose |\n|----------|-----|---------|\n| Algolia DocSearch | `https://docsearch.algolia.com/` | Search API credentials |\n| GitHub Pages | `https://pages.github.com/` | Static site hosting |\n| Mermaid CDN | `https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mermaid` | Diagram rendering |\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\n### Docusaurus Initialization\n\n```bash\nnpx create-docusaurus@latest docs classic --typescript\ncd docs\nnpm install @docusaurus/plugin-search-local\n```\n\n### Configuration Values\n\n| Field | Value |\n|-------|-------|\n| `title` | `AgentCube` |\n| `tagline` | `Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration for AI agents` |\n| `url` | `https://volcano-sh.github.io` |\n| `baseUrl` | `/agentcube/` |\n| `organizationName` | `volcano-sh` |\n| `projectName` | `agentcube` |\n| `favicon` | `img/favicon.ico` |\n| `defaultLocale` | `en` |\n\n### Sidebar Position Strategy\n\nDocuments use frontmatter `sidebar_position` for ordering:\n\n```markdown\n---\nid: installation\ntitle: Installation\nsidebar_position: 1\n---\n```\n\n### Mermaid Diagram Integration\n\nDocusaurus supports Mermaid diagrams in markdown:\n\n```markdown\n```mermaid\ngraph TD\n    A[Client] --> B[Router]\n    B --> C[WorkloadManager]\n    C --> D[K8s API]\n```\n```\n\n### Search Configuration Priority\n\n1. Algolia DocSearch (if credentials available)\n2. Local search plugin (fallback)\n\n```typescript\nthemeConfig: {\n  algolia: {\n    appId: process.env.ALGOLIA_APP_ID,\n    apiKey: process.env.ALGOLIA_API_KEY,\n    indexName: 'agentcube',\n  },\n}\n\nplugins: [\n  require.resolve('@docusaurus/plugin-search-local'),\n]\n```\n\n### Makefile Integration\n\n```makefile\n.PHONY: docs docs-start docs-clean\n\ndocs:\n\tcd docs && npm run build\n\ndocs-start:\n\tcd docs && npm run start\n\ndocs-clean:\n\trm -rf docs/build docs/.docusaurus docs/node_modules\n```\n\n### GitHub Actions Workflow\n\n```yaml\nname: Docs\n\non:\n  push:\n    branches: [main]\n    paths: ['docs/**']\n  pull_request:\n    paths: ['docs/**']\n\njobs:\n  build:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n      - uses: actions/setup-node@v4\n        with:\n          node-version: '18'\n          cache: 'npm'\n          cache-dependency-path: 'docs/package-lock.json'\n      - run: cd docs && npm ci\n      - run: cd docs && npm run build\n      - uses: actions/upload-pages-artifact@v3\n        with:\n          path: docs/build\n\n  deploy:\n    needs: build\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    if: github.event_name == 'push'\n    permissions:\n      pages: write\n      id-token: write\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/deploy-pages@v4\n```\n\n---\n\n## Validation Checklist\n\n- [x] Docusaurus project initialized with TypeScript template\n- [x] `docusaurus.config.ts` contains all required fields\n- [x] Navbar items link to valid documentation routes\n- [x] Sidebar categories and items resolve correctly\n- [x] Architecture pages render with Mermaid diagrams\n- [x] API reference pages include working code examples\n- [x] Deployment guide documents Kubernetes and Helm\n- [x] Getting started pages follow logical sequence\n- [x] Changelog page lists releases correctly\n- [x] Search integration configured (Algolia + local fallback)\n- [x] i18n directories initialized for zh-Hans\n- [x] GitHub Actions workflow triggers on docs changes\n- [x] Homepage renders with hero and CTA buttons\n- [x] Custom CSS applies branding styles\n- [x] Makefile docs targets defined\n- [x] Local dev server starts on port 3000\n- [x] Build output in `docs/build/` is valid static site\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- Spec: `changes/AR-042/spec.md`\n- Delta Spec: `changes/AR-042/delta-spec.md`\n- Proposal: `changes/AR-042/proposal.md`\n- Tasks: `changes/AR-042/tasks.md`\n- [Docusaurus Official Docs](https://docusaurus.io/docs)\n- [Docusaurus TypeScript Support](https://docusaurus.io/docs/typescript)\n- [Algolia DocSearch](https://docsearch.algolia.com/)\n- [GitHub Pages Deployment](https://docusaurus.io/docs/deployment#github-pages)\n- Source docs: `design.md`, `sandbox-orchestration/design.md`, `deployment/design.md`\n- SDK sources: `sdk-python/`, `client-go/`"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-042/design.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-042/design.md","time":{"start":1775904302346,"end":1775904302386}}}}
